title: Episode 32: Pickle Brains
description:
Ms. Pat talks about the time roaches saved her life. She gives advice to white people and black people, mainly stop killing people over Popeyes chicken sandwiches. Garrianna is back and in trouble for cursing. We are back at Ms. Pat’s house so except some kids to get yelled at. She then teaches everyone how to save money while shopping.

See Ms. Pat LIVE in St. Louis 11/22 and 11/23 at Blue Room Comedy Club
